00:25:32.329 --> 00:25:41.329
What at first seemed quite negative, the loss of trial turned out to be an amazing result. Let me give you just one example.

00:25:41.329 --> 00:25:48.329
In one of the appeals as we were presenting the appeal, not not long into the case, the appeal court judge stopped us.

00:25:48.329 --> 00:25:54.329
And he began to ask us many questions about about the Bible, about what Jehovah's Witnesses believe.

00:25:54.329 --> 00:26:03.329
So for quite some time, we answered these biblical questions. And then the case continued. And then after some minutes, the judge stopped us again.

00:26:03.329 --> 00:26:15.329
And this time the judge said, I remember reading in the Bible, the judge said this, I remember reading in the Bible that Jesus said, if they have persecuted me, they will persecute you also.

00:26:15.329 --> 00:26:19.329
So we said to the judge, yes, indeed, that Jesus said that.

00:26:19.329 --> 00:26:29.329
